This paper focuses on data management and query optimization, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also deals with complexity analysis and algorithm design, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The problem of resilience and responsibility also involves understanding the causal relationships between data, which is relevant to the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR). Finally, the paper uses formal logic and graph theory to analyze the problem, which are common tools in the field of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS).
